title: Agent@Home Travel Summit Day One: Supplier Workshops
text:
Last updated: 10:36 PM ET, Thu September 17 2015 Agent@Home Travel Summit Day One: Supplier Workshops Travel Agent | Theresa Norton Masek | September 17, 2015 
PHOTO: Drew Daly, of CruiseOne/Cruises Inc., interacted with traveling agents during this session. (Photo by Theresa Norton Masek) 
Travel agents received valuable advice on boosting their business as well as product knowledge from two well-known suppliers during afternoon workshops on the first day of the Agent@Home Travel Summit.
